Pre-Game Insights: Sunil Chhetri will lead the Indian Football Team against Australia in the AFC Asian Cup on January 13, 2024.
The match will take place at the Ahmed bin Ali Stadium.
India is placed in a tough group with Australia, Syria, and Uzbekistan.
Sunil Chhetri and Gurpreet Singh Sandhu are expected to be crucial in establishing India's hopes against Australia.
The game is anticipated to be a close one as both teams want to establish an early lead in Group B.
